replies.bodyText:
@ibacher I don't think we can do that. That's because FHIR itself doesn't allow given and family for the person resource.
http://hl7.org/implement/standards/fhir/person.html
That's why we don't have Person.SP_GIVEN or Person.SP_FAMILY available.

